Pod per Nodes


Node Network: Infra : underlay  172.31.41.155

Pod Network:  overlay Network:  192.168.0.0/16

3) Kubernetes Api  basically break your network into small small network . then  it put  on
  each worker Node. Api basically does subnet based on /26 cidr .according  it place
   small network on each worker.


4) calico basically  create route table as well on each worker .

5) all nodes's calico swaitch are connected through tunl0  ports.

